HEADWORD: Monkish
<hw>Monk"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like a monk, or pertaining to
monks; monastic; <as>as, <ex>monkish</ex> manners; <ex>monkish</ex>
dress; <ex>monkish</ex> solitude.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Monk"ish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

